  Fenicia<B style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>,</B> y
  <SPAN class=SpellE>Cipro</SPAN><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>,</B>
  y
  <SPAN class=SpellE>Antioqu&iacute;a</SPAN><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>,</B>
